---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="You're on the list · Rack & Roster"
  description="Confirmation that you're signed up for new notes."
>
  <article class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-6 py-12 sm:py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Got it. Talk soon.</h1>

    <div class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-lg leading-relaxed text-neutral-800">
      <p>
        I'll send the next note when it posts. If something from the site landed, or if you've already got a story from your own floor, write me at <a href="mailto:stephen@rackandroster.com" class="underline underline-offset-4 hover:text-neutral-600">stephen@rackandroster.com</a>. I read everything.
      </p>
    </div>

    <p class="mt-10">
      <a href="/notes" class="underline underline-offset-4 hover:text-neutral-600">[ Read the notes &rarr; ]</a>
    </p>
  </article>
</Base>
